summary: Conversion of ME3's Reckoner Bikini for the Touched by Dibella body replacer.
descriptionHtml:
This is just the conversion to the Touched by Dibella body replacer of Mass Effect 3's Reckoner Bikini, by Xinavro.
(Original download is from a JP website, so i couldn't find anymore information)


Please note that only the bikini has been converted, not the armour (gauntlets/boots/helmet should work)

Touched by Dibella body mod by themilkdrinker is required!
author: Xinavro
